On the news this evening, the election update for Council Election of
April/March 2001. Here's the latest update:

People running for council:

rAuq (has all the support he needs)
Roborick (has all the support he needs)
KSLawdogg (has all the support he needs)
Icedemon (has all the support he needs)
Megan (has all the support she needs)
Rudrak (needs one more supporter)

People who other people supported, but who have not informed me that
they're running (well, not after I announced it officially):

Kinger
Alloran (rumor has it you're not running, Alloran, but people are
still supporting you)
JP


So, if you got support and you're not running, please clear it up with
everyone, and if you need more support, try to look for some. I think
we should forget about the due date and keep this going untill its all
figured out. The first time can be hectic.
